{"tid":1154012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一分手就出post係咩心態?","createTime":"2019-05-14T04:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T05:43:54.000Z","uid":252578,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d4cfc801a621d09ef2b14174f9e63bcbf0d69e4","tid":1154012,"uid":252578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"有個拍左幾年既男朋友<br />\n初時拍拖一直都冇問題，但慢慢大家嘈交多過傾計，見面又愈黎愈少<br />\n之前一星期見一次，到後來兩至三個星期先見得一次<br />\n愈拍愈心淡，有時覺得自己好似同緊個虛疑人物拍拖咁<br />\n搵佢傾，一次過講哂自己諗咩比佢知，又話摸唔透我<br />\n結果我忍唔住，同佢講分手<br />\n第二日起身，發現佢出左分手post<br />\n個下真係頂左出黎，分手即時出post係咩心態，究竟有冇諗過我感受? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口話愛我，其實一直都係等緊我講分手，而佢自己就唔洗做衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda318e6005874f24ed37c0249d73b85f145bb16","tid":1154012,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"又係你講分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4755da572b5dc178aa118eb5e55ca6d46ab5a320","tid":1154012,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"又係你講分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fd062e8e7abfe3b9e6774de7f541c0e28940ac","tid":1154012,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"188698a08a1e04941d384de8e0f27e7016a108c3","tid":1154012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你講分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d6132441b15681bd54d5e54429447b2a15b3433","tid":1154012,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"又係你講分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7aacd26a18c9402522d11ce2236c31427e7001","tid":1154012,"uid":99086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"分手你講 光環又想拎埋 你都幾著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b85ed32b4fe1affe75c63a5eb543ef5acbc2dac","tid":1154012,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"又係你講分手既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c97569f25bb239c54f76aba186b57cae15fd85","tid":1154012,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"分手出post有咩問題<br />\n有無見過呢頭分手 呢頭第二個一齊"},{"pid":"97f1652005a43725df8c0afb84c0c4942500cc53","tid":1154012,"uid":148474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"唔係想係呢個時候打擊你，但佢只係出post，又唔係出pool<br />\n先唔講邊個提出分手，但你地兩個人之間嘅問題究竟有無真係坐低面對面好好咁傾過？<br />\n如果傾完結果都係咁，就算邊個提出分手，分手後有無出post，我諗呢啲都唔會係你宜家需要考慮嘅事。你要思考嘅，應該係究竟你地兩個人有咩問題存在。"}]}